# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AEP Dashboard — Docker Build Context Exclusions
#
# The Docker build context is the entire repo root (`.`).
# Anything listed here is NOT sent to the Docker daemon during `docker build`.
# This keeps build context small and prevents secrets leaking into the image.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets — never ever in the image ────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example   # keep example files — they're documentation, not secrets

# ── Frontend (Next.js) — not needed in the backend image ─────────────────────
dashboard/frontend/
.next/
node_modules/

# ── Python virtual environments ───────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.Python

# ── Test artifacts — results, screenshots, logs ───────────────────────────────
# NOTE: automation/ source code IS included (needed by Celery workers).
# Only generated output is excluded.
automation/results/
automation/screenshots/
automation/logs/
automation/output.xml
automation/report.html
automation/log.html
**/*.mp4           # video recordings from test runs

# ── Python build artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
**/.eggs/

# ── Editor and OS noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Git — no history needed in the image ─────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ── CI/CD config — not needed at runtime ─────────────────────────────────────
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml

# ── Docker files themselves ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (Docker doesn't need to copy itself into the image)
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# ── Docs and non-code ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTE: Do NOT exclude alembic/ README.md — alembic looks for it at runtime.
# Only exclude top-level docs.
README.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
LICENSE
docs/
